{"id":615719,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/晖思不可-4g网络正在降速/","date":"2019-08-19T09:20:32Z","modified":"2019-08-19T09:20:32Z","title":"晖思不可 | 4G网络正在降速","content":"<p>今天，我想跟你们大家聊聊国内4G网络降速这事，老规矩，还是用证据说话。</p>\n<p>最近有网友在后台向我反应，4G网络在偷偷降速了。不管是用电信4G还是移动4G，打开网页都会延迟。</p>\n<p>而且遇到这样问题的网友不是一个两个，而是有好些网友，我才意识到这不是手机本身的问题，而是4G网络的问题。</p>\n<p>这是网友在QQ聊天群里反映出来的情况</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/f3b8c2ab-f8e6-4ed7-b0d1-b50fc906860d.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-615720\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/f3b8c2ab-f8e6-4ed7-b0d1-b50fc906860d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/f3b8c2ab-f8e6-4ed7-b0d1-b50fc906860d.jpg 448w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/f3b8c2ab-f8e6-4ed7-b0d1-b50fc906860d-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" /></a></p>\n<p>6月时已有消息传来，相关部门想在8月实现5G网络的商业化运营。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615721\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976.png 1037w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976-300x61.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976-768x157.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/7eaf3637-de2a-46f9-ac61-a70b89c9f976-1024x209.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友对此的评价是，强行升级5G，这操作很是风骚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615722\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"94\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c.png 1057w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c-300x51.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c-768x132.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/9f4c88fa-a69b-4de1-9bef-c31e2e352c8c-1024x175.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>已经在网友在提出疑问：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/94b6c3a7-3635-4054-b8e8-ad831505d2a8.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615723\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/94b6c3a7-3635-4054-b8e8-ad831505d2a8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/94b6c3a7-3635-4054-b8e8-ad831505d2a8.png 997w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/94b6c3a7-3635-4054-b8e8-ad831505d2a8-300x66.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/94b6c3a7-3635-4054-b8e8-ad831505d2a8-768x168.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这个消息一出，牵动了很多网友的心，毕竟事关每一个人，每个人的手机都离不开4G网络。</p>\n<p>为此现在有很多网友在百度上搜索手机4G网络变慢的原因。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8ddc4c17-98b7-4075-b393-59bf42a7ee4f.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615724\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8ddc4c17-98b7-4075-b393-59bf42a7ee4f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"115\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8ddc4c17-98b7-4075-b393-59bf42a7ee4f.png 631w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8ddc4c17-98b7-4075-b393-59bf42a7ee4f-300x63.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>经网友实测，发现还真是这样的，理论的4G网络速度应该是100Mbps，折合为12.5M/s，但实际速度只有1.51M/s，整整差了11M/s。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18a38b48-7207-42a9-8f02-094302832124.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615725\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18a38b48-7207-42a9-8f02-094302832124.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18a38b48-7207-42a9-8f02-094302832124.jpg 636w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18a38b48-7207-42a9-8f02-094302832124-300x259.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这样的实测，有现实生活体验为基础，很多人都有这样的体会，现在的4G网速越来越慢了，去年4G网速可以达到50Mbps左右，今年以来一直在10Mbps左右徘徊。</p>\n<p>对于这个事实，新华网的文章也予以确认，并提高到了损害用户合法权益的高度。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1a9c2fc2-307e-4593-ba76-112e64a01f84.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615726\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1a9c2fc2-307e-4593-ba76-112e64a01f84.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"125\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1a9c2fc2-307e-4593-ba76-112e64a01f84.png 735w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/1a9c2fc2-307e-4593-ba76-112e64a01f84-300x68.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>目前的4G网络的理论速度，中国联通的最高下载可达15M/s，中国电信4G+为28M/s，中国移动最高为8M/s，这是三大运营商4G网络上传与下载理论速度。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8c1b79f4-488c-49bb-8375-10200972bc9d.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-615727\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8c1b79f4-488c-49bb-8375-10200972bc9d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"236\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8c1b79f4-488c-49bb-8375-10200972bc9d.png 548w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8c1b79f4-488c-49bb-8375-10200972bc9d-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然而实际速度并没有达到这么高，移动是这样，电信也是这样。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bbb700ae-5fb9-4183-a78e-543a6f428942.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615728\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bbb700ae-5fb9-4183-a78e-543a6f428942.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bbb700ae-5fb9-4183-a78e-543a6f428942.jpg 601w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/bbb700ae-5fb9-4183-a78e-543a6f428942-300x189.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ebd244bb-40f8-4c66-9561-4be7c817bcc9.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615729\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ebd244bb-40f8-4c66-9561-4be7c817bcc9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ebd244bb-40f8-4c66-9561-4be7c817bcc9.jpg 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ebd244bb-40f8-4c66-9561-4be7c817bcc9-300x178.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/ebd244bb-40f8-4c66-9561-4be7c817bcc9-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>理论速度与实际速度相差这么多，只能认为运营商是在有意降低网速。</p>\n<p>豆瓣网友也说现在4G网络速度变慢了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8a5557ba-f0dd-4d3e-896d-a5774c556caa.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615730\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8a5557ba-f0dd-4d3e-896d-a5774c556caa.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"126\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8a5557ba-f0dd-4d3e-896d-a5774c556caa.png 919w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8a5557ba-f0dd-4d3e-896d-a5774c556caa-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/8a5557ba-f0dd-4d3e-896d-a5774c556caa-768x176.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18346e9a-783a-44ea-8c09-50da1ab4af84.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615731\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18346e9a-783a-44ea-8c09-50da1ab4af84.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"102\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18346e9a-783a-44ea-8c09-50da1ab4af84.png 986w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18346e9a-783a-44ea-8c09-50da1ab4af84-300x55.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/18346e9a-783a-44ea-8c09-50da1ab4af84-768x142.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友说在有些时候，手机4G网络等于3G，甚至2G网络了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c30024ee-c324-4a6a-82af-df8f524a87e8.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615732\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c30024ee-c324-4a6a-82af-df8f524a87e8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"100\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c30024ee-c324-4a6a-82af-df8f524a87e8.png 972w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c30024ee-c324-4a6a-82af-df8f524a87e8-300x54.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c30024ee-c324-4a6a-82af-df8f524a87e8-768x139.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而且就最近这两个月的事。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/71308952-c8b4-41d3-b489-2b68e8567881.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615733\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/71308952-c8b4-41d3-b489-2b68e8567881.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"137\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/71308952-c8b4-41d3-b489-2b68e8567881.png 998w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/71308952-c8b4-41d3-b489-2b68e8567881-300x75.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/71308952-c8b4-41d3-b489-2b68e8567881-768x192.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>现在不只是4G的速度慢，电信的WIFI速度也慢。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c6845725-d15e-4b1c-b4b3-46afce9580f0.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615734\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c6845725-d15e-4b1c-b4b3-46afce9580f0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"197\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c6845725-d15e-4b1c-b4b3-46afce9580f0.png 992w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c6845725-d15e-4b1c-b4b3-46afce9580f0-300x107.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c6845725-d15e-4b1c-b4b3-46afce9580f0-768x275.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有网友用手机看视频变卡，打电话给联通，联通说这是正常情况。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a20c4058-086d-4912-9393-ba7b569bb439.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615735\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a20c4058-086d-4912-9393-ba7b569bb439.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"119\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a20c4058-086d-4912-9393-ba7b569bb439.png 965w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a20c4058-086d-4912-9393-ba7b569bb439-300x65.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a20c4058-086d-4912-9393-ba7b569bb439-768x166.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>对此，专家的意见是：中国4G技术已经到极限，4G基站已经到顶不能再建了，只能新建5G基站。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/0b227829-555d-44ee-968a-3847c0c3f19f.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615736\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/0b227829-555d-44ee-968a-3847c0c3f19f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"132\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/0b227829-555d-44ee-968a-3847c0c3f19f.png 905w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/0b227829-555d-44ee-968a-3847c0c3f19f-300x72.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/0b227829-555d-44ee-968a-3847c0c3f19f-768x184.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友不认同这样的意见，反驳道：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/15d3ce2b-e02a-4225-a22a-037b9537f2ea.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615737\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/15d3ce2b-e02a-4225-a22a-037b9537f2ea.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"166\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/15d3ce2b-e02a-4225-a22a-037b9537f2ea.png 985w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/15d3ce2b-e02a-4225-a22a-037b9537f2ea-300x90.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/15d3ce2b-e02a-4225-a22a-037b9537f2ea-768x232.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有网友解释称，说现在各家运营商都推出无限流量套餐了，大家时刻在用流量，所以手机网速变慢了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a616fc17-852e-4698-87ec-190cbeddfd00.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615738\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a616fc17-852e-4698-87ec-190cbeddfd00.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"107\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a616fc17-852e-4698-87ec-190cbeddfd00.png 727w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/a616fc17-852e-4698-87ec-190cbeddfd00-300x59.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有网友解释称，说现在各家运营商都推出无限流量套餐了，大家时刻在用流量，所以手机网速变慢了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b30a3d0a-7f0c-43ef-8712-cacd871a527d.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615739\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b30a3d0a-7f0c-43ef-8712-cacd871a527d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"165\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b30a3d0a-7f0c-43ef-8712-cacd871a527d.png 991w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b30a3d0a-7f0c-43ef-8712-cacd871a527d-300x90.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/b30a3d0a-7f0c-43ef-8712-cacd871a527d-768x231.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>对此，也有网友反驳道：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2e394ee8-ba58-49dd-9423-3a4f3344b902.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615740\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2e394ee8-ba58-49dd-9423-3a4f3344b902.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"134\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2e394ee8-ba58-49dd-9423-3a4f3344b902.png 988w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2e394ee8-ba58-49dd-9423-3a4f3344b902-300x73.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/2e394ee8-ba58-49dd-9423-3a4f3344b902-768x187.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友就5G发展，还提出这样的几个疑问：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/629a3143-601f-4682-aa6c-f9da26f06a1a.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615741\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/629a3143-601f-4682-aa6c-f9da26f06a1a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"156\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/629a3143-601f-4682-aa6c-f9da26f06a1a.png 661w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/629a3143-601f-4682-aa6c-f9da26f06a1a-300x85.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有一种观点，说4G变速，是因为5G的测试用户挤占了4G用户的空间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c1c2578b-cc5d-434c-88c8-9e08188d90f6.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-615742\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c1c2578b-cc5d-434c-88c8-9e08188d90f6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"74\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c1c2578b-cc5d-434c-88c8-9e08188d90f6.png 658w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c1c2578b-cc5d-434c-88c8-9e08188d90f6-300x41.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/c1c2578b-cc5d-434c-88c8-9e08188d90f6-220x30.png 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这样一来，5G网络让人要又喜又忧了，因为有政策在强力推动。</p>\n<p>不管是怎样的原因，反正以后的4G网速会越来越慢，原因是：</p>\n<p>运营商现在的重心都会放在接下来的5G和5G基站建设方面，在4G方面的建设也就会继续放缓，甚至暂时停止。也就是4G网络速度越来越慢的情况会继续恶化，并且无法得到改善。</p>\n<p>是不是因为5G要来，所以降低4G网速呢？这里我不好揣测，可是如今4G网速确实下降，这对于用户来说还是相当不方便的，极大的影响4G体验，这样下来，又何谈良好的用户体验，又谈何为用户着想，满足用户需求为上的服务素养呢？</p>\n<p>我建议移动电信等运营商能够做好4G网络结构，不管5G是否普及，维护好用户上网速度，这个本职工作不能丢。</p>\n<p>毕竟，把用户放在心上，保证用户良好的4G网络速度，这样的移动联通电信三大公司才是值得尊敬的。否则，哪怕赚再多的钱，也是得不到用户们一毛钱的信任和欢喜，相反三大运营商赚钱越多，用户的怒气值就越高。</p>\n<p>就算从法律层面上来说，用户与运营商之间是一个契约关系。用户一次性购买手机套餐后，按说运营商要提供合格的服务，即使网速没有提高，也不能放慢，否则就是一种违约行为。这点对于三大运营商是适用的，对工信部也是适用的。</p>\n<p>那样一来，移动电信联通又凭什么来获取公众的尊重呢？想推广5G可以，但不能牺牲4G用户的上网速度。</p>\n<p>这就是我的观点，也是我的态度。</p>\n<p>(有删节)</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[38717,37176,38719,38718,22649]}